OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1778328667
OL,3,CSouthampton charged with spying by EFL
OL,4,Cahead of play-off against Middlesbrough
OL,6,FSouthampton have been charged with a
OL,7,Fbreach of EFL regulations after being
OL,8,Faccused of spying on a Middlesbrough
OL,9,Ftraining session ahead of the two
OL,10,Fclubs' Championship play-off semi-
OL,11,Ffinal.
OL,13,FThe English Football League (EFL) had
OL,14,Freceived a complaint from
OL,15,FMiddlesbrough over allegations of
OL,16,Funauthorised filming by someone
OL,17,Fconnected to Southampton during a
OL,18,Ftraining session ahead of Saturday's
OL,19,F(9 May) first leg at the Riverside
OL,20,FStadium.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
